# Elevate Apparel Brand Theme

Follow the full theme spec in [CLAUDE.md](../../CLAUDE.md) (**Elevate Apparel Brand Theme**). Homepage is the approved reference. Storefront **and** admin must match this system.

## Fonts

- UI: Geist Sans (`font-sans`)
- Editorial only: Playfair Display (`font-serif`)
- Mono rare: Geist Mono (`font-mono`)
- Do not introduce Inter/Roboto/system as the brand face

## Colors (canonical — do not drift)

| Role           | Hex       |
| -------------- | --------- |
| Background     | `#FAFAFA` |
| Primary text   | `#111111` |
| Secondary text | `#555555` |
| Accent         | `#C9A227` |
| Accent hover   | `#D4B03A` |
| Border         | `#E5E7EB` |
| Cards          | `#FFFFFF` |

Tokens: `frontend/app/globals.css`, `frontend/lib/design-system.ts` (`DS`, `btnPrimary`, `btnSecondary`, `cardShell`).

Do **not** use the old dark palette (`#0a0a0b`, `#111110`, `#1a1815`, `#e3bb78`, etc.).

## Buttons

- **Primary:** `#111111` + white text → hover `#C9A227` + black text
- **Secondary:** white + black border → hover black fill + white text

## Navbar & footer

- Navbar: sticky `#FAFAFA`, soft shadow, text/icons `#111111`, active/hover gold
- Footer (storefront only): stays **dark** — black bg, white text, gold headings
- Logo: use `BrandLogo` only — `on="light"` on light chrome, `on="dark"` on footer/dark sections; never inside a fixed black/white box

## UI patterns

- Max width `1400px`
- Sharp radii (`rounded-[4px]`–`rounded-lg`), not pill-heavy
- Uppercase compact CTAs; gold focus rings
- Light-first; no purple/indigo glow themes; no cream broadsheet defaults
- Soft alerts: green / gold / red / blue for success / warning / error / info

When building or restyling any page, reuse header/footer/auth/homepage/admin-shell visual language.
